| accessdate = 2010-06-20}}</ref> finishing the season with three appearances.<ref name="Northampton 2000/2001 player appearances"/> He signed a first two-year [[professional]] contract with the club in April 2004.<ref name="PFA 109"/><ref name="Who Are Ya?">{{cite news
