===Bristol Rovers===
After returning he only managed to play one league game before being loaned out again to [[Football League Two|League Two]] team [[Bristol Rovers F.C.|Bristol Rovers]] until the end of the season on 24 March.<ref name="Games played by Chris Carruthers in 2004/2005">{{cite web
